DESCRIPTION:Worship starts at 7pm\n\nSoulful Sundown is an alternative sty
 le worship led by young adults on the second Sunday of every month. Servic
 es are held at sunset around the fire pit\, weather permitting. The servic
 es are each based around a central theme and include music\, movement\, an
 d art. General participation is encouraged.  A potluck of finger foods is 
 held before each service. Come early and get to know everyone! For more in
 formation look for our poster and fliers in the Great Hall or contact Tom 
 Zolot.
LOCATION:UU Church of Davis\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, Davis\, CA
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
