BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:MH - Xmas Eve Worship
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20081224T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20081224T200000
UID:1n2c1o4pnos0p3ftm8ougjpe0g@google.com
DESCRIPTION:The Dawning of our Dreams\, This traditional service is filled
  with carols\, readings\, and music. We tell the story of our humanness an
 d our hope for the future. Often in the midst of darkness\, when we think 
 all is lost\, there comes a great light. To enact the coming of hope\, can
 dlelight will be added to our sanctuary. We’ll ends with a candlelight r
 ecessional and the recognition of our part in becoming the light of the fu
 ture.\n\nSpecial Collection: Community Involvement Committee (CIC) – Bot
 h Dec. 24 offerings will benefit the UUCD CIC\, which works for social jus
 tice in Davis through\, Davis Community Meals\, Adopt a Social Worker\, Pr
 ogress Ranch and Campus Ministry! Please help them to run their important 
 programs all year by donating generously Dec. 24. Make check out to “UUC
 D\,” memo “CIC.”
LOCATION:Unitarian Universalist Church of Davis\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, Davis 
 CA 95616
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
