BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:LIB - Rowing into the Falls
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20080927T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20080927T210000
UID:lvcu392rbfabhbhlod7qi7jd50@google.com
DESCRIPTION:Worship 7:30-8:30pm Rev. Beth Banks & Elaine Aron.\n\n\nRowing
  to the Falls: This service is specifically for the parents who are in tra
 nsition because their children are graduating or moving on to another stag
 e of life. Most parents who attend have children who are graduating from h
 igh school\, but there are also parents whose children are entering fifth 
 grade\, or parents whose children are leaving for the Peace Corps. Friends
  have started to bring friends\, and it’s becoming a caring community ou
 treach. Sometimes we invite a parent to speak whose child graduated from H
 S the previous year.
LOCATION:UUCD\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, 95616
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
