UID:bhm9omjpdouchpon13ue3b7oh0@google.com
DESCRIPTION:Potluck at 6pm\, worship at 6:30pm\n\nSoulful Sundown is an al
 ternative style worship led by young adults on the second Sunday of every 
 month. Services are held at sunset around the fire pit\, weather permittin
 g. The services are each based around a central theme and include music\, 
 movement\, and art. General participation is encouraged.  A potluck of fin
 ger foods is held before each service. Come early and get to know everyone
 ! For more information look for our poster and fliers in the Great Hall or
  contact Brittany Hernandez.
LOCATION:UU Church of Davis\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, Davis\, CA
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
