BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:New Worship Schedule!
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20090118
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20090119
UID:n1ehmi23cgu9hrko96u4t1pe70@google.com
DESCRIPTION:Starting today\, Worship is as follows (parallel times for RE)
 : \n\nEvery Sunday…\n\nLife Journey\n9:30 – 10:15am\nConnection and Re
 newal\n         • Sermon illuminated by congregant’s life journey refl
 ection\n         • Milestones with spoken joys and sorrows \n         
 • Soloists and instrumentalists shape the mood\n         • Connections
  deepened at this 45 minute worship\n \nSpirited Worship\n10:30 – 11am\n
 Move. Show. Sing. Laugh. \n         • Have fun together at this all-ages
  celebration!\n         • Worship message enacted more than spoken\n    
      • Families and ministers lead worship\n         • Physical moveme
 nt encouraged\, but not required\n         • Rousing traditional and con
 temporary songs of Unitarian Universalism\n \nRising in Spirit\n11:15am 
 – 12:15pm\nReflection and Inspiration\n         • Sermon enriched by W
 orship Associate’s inspirational reflection\n         • Generous weavi
 ng of music with Chalice Choir and Dance Choir or other liturgical arts\n 
         • Full-spirited congregational singing\n         • All-embraci
 ng community pastoral prayer\n\nOnce a month: Soulful Sundown\nSecond Sund
 ays at Sundown\; meet us at the fire pit\, weather permitting\nEarth-Cente
 red\,  Alternative Worship\n         •Variety\; each service is unique a
 nd has a central theme\n         •Worship is led by young adults\, but E
 VERYONE is invited!\n         •Join us for music\, movement\, art\n     
     •Come early for a finger-food potluck and community-building chat\n 
         •Active participation is encouraged!
LOCATION:UU Church of Davis\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, Davis\, CA
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
