BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Worship: Gathering the Waters
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20080907T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20080907T100000
UID:ulus0j5elul55leatkkne002ug@google.com
DESCRIPTION:9-10am and 11-noon All Ages Worship: Gathering the Waters with
  Rev. Elizabeth O. Banks. This summer\, please remember to bring a small c
 ontainer of water that will represent your journey. More than celebrating 
 the distance in miles\, we will honor what the summer’s experiences mean
  to you.\n\n*No Spirited Worship/ No Children’s Religious Exploration\n\
 nThis is our yearly welcome back worship with the gathering of the waters 
 from summer experiences.  Young Adult\, Catlyn LeGault will be narrating a
  re-authored version of The Giving Tree. Worship Associates will be encour
 aged to model adult participation during the story.\nAdditional Informatio
 n: Our Intern\, Elaine Aron will be introduced during the service. There w
 ill be a special celebration following the second worship – the recipien
 ts don’t know they’re the honored guests. BIG secret and BIG recogniti
 on.
LOCATION:Unitarian Universalist Church of Davis\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, Davis 
 CA 95616
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
