SUMMARY:MB - Keys to Hunger Benefit Concert for Food Bank of Yolo Cty
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20121027T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20121027T220000
UID:5ettf4653oknk3i5diu25vq43k@google.com
DESCRIPTION:Shawn Marie Kramer\nCommunity Relations Manager\nFood Bank of 
 Yolo County\n(530) 668-0690 x 106\n<http://foodbankyc.org/>\n\nFeaturing S
 andra Brown & Helen Twiss - piano duets\nAll proceeds of the concert will 
 benefit FBYC. The following is a breakdown of ticket prices for the event:
 \nStudent w/ID\, $10\nAdult\, $20\nFamily\, $30 \n\nThe mission of FBYC is
  to alleviate hunger and malnutrition in Yolo County. Through our programs
  and partnerships with more than 60 member agencies\, approximately 20\,00
 0 residents are served each month. In addition\, FBYC is committed to nutr
 ition and has increased access to fresh fruits and vegetables and works to
  educate the community on the benefits of eating healthy. In 2011\, one-th
 ird of the food distributed by FBYC was fresh produce.
LOCATION:UU Church of Davis\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, Davis\, CA
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
