BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Virtual Auction Begins
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20081010
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20081011
UID:uj0p66k0jpkgr3q9lk6o888tnc@google.com
DESCRIPTION:Virtual Auction\n\nWelcome to the second year of the Virtual A
 uction! Our first year raised approximately the same amount of money as th
 e traditional live auction\, but with only 5% of the volunteer effort. Not
  bad for starters! And with virtual auctions in fall and spring\, there ar
 e twice as many chances for you to meet new church members\, enjoy the com
 pany of small groups\, and support our church financially!\n\nThe auction 
 catalog is posted at www.uudavis.org\, e-mailed to church members\, and av
 ailable in printed form. Purchasers contact the donor directly to buy a se
 rvice or space at an event. We even have a “Wish\nList” where you stat
 e what you’d like to purchase and a donor calls you to offer that item.\
 n\nOur Fall 2008 Auction begins October 10\n(for events from January 1 - J
 une 30\, 2009)\n\nTo donate a service or event\, or put something on the 
 “Wish List\,” please contact: Linda Magrum.
LOCATION:UU Church of Davis\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, Davis\, CA
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
