UID:1b6gfacb18u7q1qbpk783nb18g@google.com
DESCRIPTION:Rev. Nancy Shaffer\, Celebration of Life\, 2pm\, Fri\, June \n
 15\, Sanctuary. Nancy was a long-time member of UUCD. \nShe was inspired b
 y Rev. David Keyes to enter ministry. \nShe served a number of congregatio
 ns\, and is well-known for her Meditation Manual\, Instructions in Joy\, \
 npublished by Skinner House Books. An additional \ncollection of her poems
 \, written during the last year of \nher life\, will be published by Skinn
 er House. Come \nhonor Nancy and her love of life.
