DESCRIPTION:Andrei Baumann in Concert\n\nJune 9\, 7pm\n\nUnitarian Univers
 alist Church of Davis\n\nPROGRAM: Bach: French Suite in C Minor\, BWV 813\
 n\nChopin: Polonaise-Fantasie in A-flat Major\, Op. 61\n\nChopin: Mazurkas
 \n\nChopin: Ballade No. 4 in F Minor\, Op. 52\n\nIntermission\n\nSpruill: 
 Music for Made-Up Movies (2018)\n\nIves: The Alcotts from the Concord Sona
 ta\n\nBeethoven: Piano Sonata in E-flat Major\, Op. 109\n\nSuggested donat
 ion $20\; concert benefits UU Church of Davis.\n\n27074 Patwin Road (off R
 ussell Blvd)\, Davis CA 95616\n\nwww.uudavis.orgmusic@uudavis.org530-753-2
 581 x203\n\nMr. Baumann is a frequent performer at the Mondavi Center\, Ha
 rris Center and has performed extensively in the USA\, Europe\, Canada and
  Venezuela. Mr. Baumann has moved back to Davis\, and is accepting student
 s. https://www.aabadventures.com/
