BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Kate's Office - ARE Committee
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20141008T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20141008T203000
UID:2rdcps9pjfpuugedo5qsuren2g@google.com
DESCRIPTION:Adult Religious Exploration Committee\nContact: Kate Raymond\n
 Mission Statement:  The purpose of the Adult Religious Exploration Committ
 ee is to facilitate and collaborate with others to create programs and res
 ources that encourage a free and responsible search for truth and meaning 
 through a variety of formats.\n\n     This committee works to fan the flam
 es of spiritual growth in our church community and to encourage a free and
  responsible search for truth. The ways we are doing this at present inclu
 de providing books for sale at the RE Table\, providing logistical support
  for our Carpe Diem workshop facilitators\, surveying the congregation to 
 assess their needs for religious exploration and then trying to provide ex
 periences to meet those needs.  If you are interested in joining this comm
 ittee to support adult religious programming\, please contact Kate Raymond
  for an application.\n\nARE meets from 7 to 8:30 p.m. on the fourth Thursd
 ay of every month.
LOCATION:UUCD\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, 95616
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
