DESCRIPTION:Grounds minus the spaces already in use\n\nComing of Age (COA)
  is now full and closed to further sign-ups.  \n\n    Every other year\, o
 ur congregation’s 8th-10th graders are asked to take their first steps i
 nto spiritual maturity through the Coming of Age program.  In partnership 
 with the Pacific Central District of the Unitarian Universalist Associatio
 n\, our congregation presents our youth with an exciting program that chal
 lenges their own limits and clarifies their values in the good \ncompany o
 f other UU youth\, their mentors and the COA facilitators.\n   This progra
 m is our UU Rite of Passage acknowledging the departure from childhood and
  requires the commitment of youth and parents to be willing to change.\n\n
 Contact Kate Raymond
LOCATION:UUCD\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, 95616
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
