BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:LIB - MBSR w/ Anne Hoffmann
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20081029T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20081029T210000
UID:ki3jde3n98lm71iqrpssruf6pc@google.com
DESCRIPTION:Intro to Mindfulness Based Stress Reduction (MBSR)\, offered 1
 0 weeks\, Wednesdays\, Sept 24 – Nov 19\, with an all-day session on Sat
 urday\, Nov 8 from 9am to 2pm.  There is a suggested donation for the clas
 s\; no one will be turned away for lack of funds.  \n\n     This class is 
 intended as a resource for your daily life.  It teaches a mindful approach
  to living that can help reduce stress\, increase quality of life\, and as
 sist in managing chronic pain.  This course is based on the work done by J
 on Kabat-Zinn at The UMASS Medical School.  (http://www.umassmed.edu/cfm/i
 ndex.aspx)  \nFacilitator:  Anne Hoffmann studied MBSR at the Medical Cent
 er with its teachers and with Jon Kabat-Zinn.  She is a long time practiti
 oner of Zen meditation and this will be the first time she is teaching thi
 s particular course.  Her background is in theatre and dance and she is a 
 graduate of Union Theological Seminary in New York City\, as well as an or
 dained minister in the United Church of Christ.
LOCATION:UUCD\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, 95616
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:SR - ARE: TIE 2
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20091104T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20091104T210000
UID:bllp7148ck93hsmuvq2003cb1o@google.com
DESCRIPTION:Together In Exploration (TIE) Small Group Ministry Group 2\n\n
 TIE Groups provide islands of community to those who might otherwise feel 
 lost in the glorious rush and complexity of life within our congregation. 
 Groups of 8 to 10 members each meet twice-monthly\, along with a trained f
 acilitator and a facilitator-in-training. Each group develops their own co
 venant of behavior in order to deepen friendships and share stories and in
 sights from their life journeys.  The group will also have the opportunity
  to decide on at least one social service project to do together. \n\nNew 
 groups will be formed each year. Sign-ups begin now for groups that meet t
 wice a month from November through June. After the first four meetings\, w
 e will ask for a commitment until June.\n\nTime:   7 – 9 pm/ First and T
 hird Wednesdays  OR  7 – 9 pm First and Third Tuesdays\n\nLocation:  Sen
 ghas Room near the Kitchen\, opposite the Sanctuary\n\nFee:  Free\n\nSign 
 up:  by sending an email to register@uudavis.org
LOCATION:UU Church of Davis\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, Davis\, CA
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
