BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:LIB - ARE: Invitation to Awakening
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20090405T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20090405T210000
UID:j2nh1ec321keidio87vffdmvls@google.com
DESCRIPTION:"An Invitation to Awakening" -- Jack Whitsett and Larry Melton
 \n\nOne of the most fundamental questions facing each of us is "Who am I?"
   Ancient Hindu tradition\, going back perhaps 6000 years\, teaches us: "T
 hou art that." What then is the "that" that thou art? We will explore the 
 path to the discovery of one's true self with reference to modern non-dual
  mystics\, including Aldous Huxley\, Ken Wilber\, Eckhart Tolle\, and Adya
 shanti.
LOCATION:UUCD\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, 95616
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
