BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:MH - Voluntarily Simple Holiday Planning
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20081116T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20081116T133000
UID:2kupnsvmukes62up9qcaoi0c04@google.com
DESCRIPTION:In Summer 2007\, a group of us gathered once a week for 6 week
 s to study a Northwest Earth Institute curriculum on "Voluntary Simplicity
 ."  We've been meeting ever since to share our paths toward the goal of a 
 simpler\, more earth-friendly and meaningful life.  Now we'd like to hold 
 a church-wide discussion on "how to take back Christmas"  -- or other holi
 days -- so that it's more meaningful and less stressful for us and our fam
 ilies. Please join us right after the 11:00 service in the Sanctuary on Su
 nday\, Nov 16\, for an interactive discussion and sharing about how to liv
 e out our UU values during the holidays (which can sometimes be a real cha
 llenge!!).  For more information\, please call Nancy Kays
LOCATION:UU Church of Davis\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, Davis\, CA
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
