BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:SR - ARE: TIE 2
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20091118T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20091118T210000
UID:oidoi3lkd6rk16g373ehhmnqgs@google.com
DESCRIPTION:Together In Exploration (TIE) Small Group Ministry Group 1\n\n
 TIE Groups provide islands of community to those who might otherwise feel 
 lost in the glorious rush and complexity of life within our congregation. 
 Groups of 8 to 10 members each meet twice-monthly\, along with a trained f
 acilitator and a facilitator-in-training. Each group develops their own co
 venant of behavior in order to deepen friendships and share stories and in
 sights from their life journeys.  The group will also have the opportunity
  to decide on at least one social service project to do together. \n\nNew 
 groups will be formed each year. Sign-ups begin now for groups that meet t
 wice a month from November through June. After the first four meetings\, w
 e will ask for a commitment until June.\n\nTime:   7 – 9 pm/ First and T
 hird Wednesdays  OR  7 – 9 pm First and Third Tuesdays\n\nLocation:  Sen
 ghas Room near the Kitchen\, opposite the Sanctuary\n\nFee:  Free\n\nSign 
 up:  by sending an email to register@uudavis.org
LOCATION:UU Church of Davis\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, Davis\, CA
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
