BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:LIB - Wilbur Workshop
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20090228T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20090228T160000
UID:tdvihp5qo80uknos3k8jnuvpao@google.com
DESCRIPTION:An Integral Perspective: Practical Application\n \nClass runs 
 10am to 3:30pm in the Church Library on Feb 28\, 2009\n\nLast spring we in
 troduced Ken Wilber’s Integral Model. This winter we’ll look at how yo
 u can apply the model to your own life as you become the change you want t
 o see in the world. Developed by Wilber and the team at Integral Institute
  \nThe Integral Life Practice (ILP) is grounded in the very best of Integr
 al Theory. The core modules are mind\, body\, spirit and shadow. In additi
 on it includes modules in ethics\, sex\, work\, emotions and relationships
 . This day long will focus on two of these aspects:\n\n•Mind. The practi
 ce of taking perspectives. We’ll have a longer look at worldviews to pro
 mote greater understanding and compassion.\n\n•Shadow. The practice of a
 ttending to parts of yourself that we’ve denied and disowned. We’ll do
  the 3-2-1 process (in writing and you don’t have to share) which you ca
 n use to increase effectiveness in all areas of life.\n\nNo worries if you
  missed the first seminar\, we’ll begin with a brief introduction of the
  Integral Model. If you want to start reading\, the new Integral Life Prac
 tice: A 21st Century Blueprint for Physical Health\, Emotional Balance\, M
 ental Clarity\, and Spiritual Awakening will be released on Sept. 9th.\n\n
 \n\n\nContact Kate Raymond
LOCATION:UUCD 27074 Patwin Rd\, 95616
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
