BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:LIB/MH/Grounds - RE Summer seasonal retreat
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20090620T070000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20090620T163000
UID:t0sic2d8hspqn0qf96mur1mioc@google.com
DESCRIPTION:Library from 7am - 2:30pm\nMeetinghouse from noon to 4:30pm\nC
 ontact Kate Raymond\n\nContact Kate Raymond\n\nA Year of Seasonal Retreats
 \n \nAn invitation to reflect on your life \nusing the metaphor of the sea
 sons\n\nNovember 1st ~ SEEDS OF TRUE SELF \nJanuary 31\, 2009 ~ DWELLING I
 N DARKNESS: \nTHE ROOT OF INNER WISDOM \nMarch 28\, 2009 ~ EMBRACING PARAD
 OX: \nBREAKING INTO BLOSSOM \nJune 20\, 2009 ~ WITHIN US AN ORCHARD \n \nL
 ocation: Unitarian Universalist Church of Davis\nTime: 8:30AM~4:00PM \nSea
 sonal lunch and refreshments will be served.\n\nEach Retreat will provide 
 the opportunity to:\nListen within ourselves\, to each other\, and to the 
 natural world\nExplore questions of meaning\, purpose\, calling\, service\
 , and the inner life\n\nSuggested donation for each retreat is $50 or $180
  for the series.\nPlease sign up by October 15th\nContact Jody Lusebrink b
 y phone (530) 758-5494\nor email seasonalretreats@gmail.com\n\nFacilitated
  by: Elizabeth Andrea\, Glen Lusebrink\, Jody Lusebrink \nand Kate Raymond
LOCATION:UUCD\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, 95616
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
