DESCRIPTION:Coming of Age (COA) is now full and closed to further sign-ups
 .  \n\n    Every other year\, our congregation’s 8th-10th graders are as
 ked to take their first steps into spiritual maturity through the Coming o
 f Age program.  In partnership with the Pacific Central District of the Un
 itarian Universalist Association\, our congregation presents our youth wit
 h an exciting program that challenges their own limits and clarifies their
  values in the good \ncompany of other UU youth\, their mentors and the CO
 A facilitators.\n   This program is our UU Rite of Passage acknowledging t
 he departure from childhood and requires the commitment of youth and paren
 ts to be willing to change.\n\nContact Kate Raymond
LOCATION:UU Church of Davis\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, Davis\, CA
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
