DESCRIPTION:UU  Childcare Co-op\n \n\nWho couldn’t use a regular night o
 ut for yourself while your child(ren) play with their friends at church! T
 hen when it’s your turn to help out other parents with their night out\,
  you get the chance to meet some other members and form your own friendshi
 ps.\n\n$5 per child\n4th Saturdays of each month from 6:30 to 10:30 p.m. \
 nat the church Bridgehouse\n\nJunior High Schoolers graciously give parent
 s a hand.\nAt least 3 adults at every event.\n\nContact Suzanne Kimmel if 
 interested
