BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:LIB - CYRE
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20080717T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20080717T210000
UID:n13vvdbtqo0ettc14gldprkvi0@google.com
DESCRIPTION:Children and Youth Religious Exploration (CYRE) Council\n\nThe
  primary principle guiding this council is the encouragement of spiritual 
 growth of the young of our congregation.  Our responsibilities include:\n\
 n·To oversee ongoing CYRE programming\, ensuring together with the DRE an
 d Youth Coordinator that such activities are well coordinated and implemen
 ted.\n·To provide RE leadership\, determining training or other support n
 eeded for volunteer teachers and staff\, input and revision of curriculum\
 , and planning special worship and community building activities.\n·To wo
 rk with the board and congregation to ensure support and approval of RE st
 ructure and programs.\n\nOur CYRE members are the ones who put on the Secr
 et Buddy program\, recruit teachers\, plan our summer programs\, lead the 
 visioning for our new RE building\, oversee the Safety policy and attend t
 o the needs of our RE families.  If you would like to be a part of this mi
 nistry to our congregation\, please contact DRE Kate Raymond or Amy Wilson
 \, CYRE chair.\n\nContact Kate Raymond
LOCATION:LIB
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
