BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:LIB/MH/Grounds - RE Winter Seasonal retreat
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20090131T070000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20090131T180000
UID:3jlu9uoc5g0asnt920pm4a95ac@google.com
DESCRIPTION:Contact Kate Raymond\n\nA Year of Seasonal Retreats\n \nAn inv
 itation to reflect on your life \nusing the metaphor of the seasons\n\nNov
 ember 1st ~ SEEDS OF TRUE SELF \nJanuary 31\, 2009 ~ DWELLING IN DARKNESS:
  \nTHE ROOT OF INNER WISDOM \nMarch 28\, 2009 ~ EMBRACING PARADOX: \nBREAK
 ING INTO BLOSSOM \nJune 20\, 2009 ~ WITHIN US AN ORCHARD \n \nLocation: Un
 itarian Universalist Church of Davis\nTime: 8:30AM~4:00PM \nSeasonal lunch
  and refreshments will be served.\n\nEach Retreat will provide the opportu
 nity to:\nListen within ourselves\, to each other\, and to the natural wor
 ld\nExplore questions of meaning\, purpose\, calling\, service\, and the i
 nner life\n\nSuggested donation for each retreat is $50 or $180 for the se
 ries.\nPlease sign up by October 15th\nContact Jody Lusebrink by phone (53
 0) 758-5494\nor email seasonalretreats@gmail.com\n\nFacilitated by: Elizab
 eth Andrea\, Glen Lusebrink\, Jody Lusebrink \nand Kate Raymond
LOCATION:UUCD\, 27074 Patwin Rd\, 95616
URL:https://uudavis.org/calendar/
X-SOURCE:UU Davis
END:VEVENT
